&lt;li&gt;Train labeling teams on product policy and communicate policy concepts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Articulate policy positions for internal teams in order to support client queries and requests.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive research on public opinions and advertiser perspectives in order to inform policy creation and policy adjustments.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Steer ongoing policy improvement prioritization based on a variety of input from a diversity of stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
