&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with web and social media content trends.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interest in and passion for policy and content classification/moderation.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Preferred Qualifications&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working in product or content policy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with national or international policy proposals or frameworks for addressing harmful content online.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with no-code and AI tools in professional settings.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with internet policy issues.&lt;/li&gt;
