&lt;li&gt;Achieve personal quarterly/annual revenue and new business targets, as agreed with the Sales Lead&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver accurate sales forecasting insight&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
